Package org.hypknowsys.wumprep.config Description

Provides classes for dealing with WUMprep configuration files in Java.

WUMprepConfiguration provides an interface for loading, modifying and saving WUMprep configuration files. It comes with WUMprepConfigurationEditor and WUMprepConfigurationCustomizer, which provide JavaBeans-conformant GUI components for manipulating WUMprepConfigurations.
